title: C# Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Japanese cafe at 長野市上ヶ屋2471-2509 specializing in onigiri (brown fermented rice). All but a few of the onigiri contain fish; otherwise all vegan. Menu has mixed vegetable plate, soup, vegan curry and lunchboxes. Makes a red bean sticky rice dessert. Traditional seating on tatami floor or takeaway to nearby walking trail through Ooyachi Wetlands adjacent to the cafe. English menu upon request.
